const requestTypes = [
  "get",
  "post",
  "put",
  "delete",
  "patch",
  "head",
  "options",
  "trace",
];

export default requestTypes;

export const locationTypes = [
  "path",
  "query",
  "header",
  "cookie"
];

export const dataTypes = [
  "boolean",
  "string",
  "integer",
  "number",
  "array",
  "object"
];

export const formatTypes = [
  "date",
  "date-time",
  "byte",
  "binary",
  "password"
];
